[MFLOG|0|2026-03-16T00:37:04.258737Z|runtime|a9ec62e4-b6fa-449c-817e-b2b46d8da1fb]Using a slow image processor as `use_fast` is unset and a slow processor was saved with this model. `use_fast=True` will be the default behavior in v4.52, even if the model was saved with a slow processor. This will result in minor differences in outputs. You'll still be able to use a slow processor with `use_fast=False`.
